The actress was been nostalgic as she talked about her background. Nkechi Blessing said she is a poor girl from the streets of Agege, Lagos whose mother sold beer and pepper soup. She wrote: “Allow me Brag about myself a little,I am still that Poor girl from the streets of AGEGE,That her mother sold bear and pepper soup to thousands of Millionaires and billionaires Today,I wasn’t Born with a silver spoon,neither am I from a very rich family,I don’t have plenty,but I know how it feels not to have at all…Here is RE_introducing you to my World and lifestyle of CHARITY as I birth my new Baby the @nbs_foundation1” See Photos: Source